2020050815411117.title: Read Me!
2020050815411117.contents:
Thanks for downloading the worlds simplest note taking app!

I developed this in response to all the note taking apps that either have too many features or the features you actually want are locked behind a paywall.

My github is linked just below the title in the top left if you feel like suggesting features, forking or need to report a bug!

Thanks, Joe B.
